videos.description: Zach Charbonnet goes up the middle for a 70-yard touchdown run vs. Minnesota.

videos.headline: Charbonnet runs for 70-yard Michigan TD

videos.description: Caden Fey flies through the Michigan line untouched and blocks the Wolverines' punt.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Minnesota blocks Michigan punt on opening drive) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Minnesota blocks Michigan punt on opening drive

videos.description: Tanner Morgan lines a pass to Ko Kieft who falls into the end zone for a 14-yard Minnesota touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Morgan connects with Kieft for 14-yard TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morgan connects with Kieft for 14-yard TD

videos.description: Michael Barrett blitzes in for the tackle on Tanner Morgan, forcing a fumble recovered by Donovan Jeter for a Michigan touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Barrett's massive hit on Morgan results in Michigan big man TDD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Barrett's massive hit on Morgan results in Michigan big man TD

videos.description: Joe Milton dumps a pass off to Ben Mason who runs and leaps into the end zone for a nine-yard touchdown vs. Minnesota.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mason dives in for 9-yard Michigan touchdown) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mason dives in for 9-yard Michigan touchdown

videos.description: Mohamed Ibrahim takes the handoff 16 yards for a Minnesota touchdown vs. Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ibrahim cuts upfield for 16-yard TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ibrahim cuts upfield for 16-yard TD

videos.description: Hassan Haskins follows blockers up the middle for a four-yard touchdown to give Michigan a 28-17 lead vs. Minnesota.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Haskins powers in for Michigan TD) 2020// ESHEET

videos.headline: Haskins powers in for Michigan TD

videos.description: Hassan Haskins takes the handoff up the middle for his second touchdown run of the game for Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Haskins runs for his second TD of first half) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haskins runs for his second TD of first half

videos.description: Mohamed Ibrahim runs up the middle for a five-yard Minnesota touchdown vs. Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ibrahim runs in for 5-yard Minnesota TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ibrahim runs in for 5-yard Minnesota TD

videos.description: Joe Milton takes the snap up the middle for a two-yard Michigan touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Milton keeps it for goal-line TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Milton keeps it for goal-line TD

videos.description: Chris Evans takes the handoff five yards for a touchdown as Michigan extends its lead over Minnesota.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Evans bounces outside for a 5-yard TD run) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Evans bounces outside for a 5-yard TD run

videos.description: Joe Milton completes 15 of 22 passes, while throwing for a touchdown and running for another in Michigan's 49-24 win vs. Minnesota.
